        <div class="TrendingHeader">Italy </div>
        <p>Italy, a country with a long Mediterranean coastline has it all. Culture, history, food, wine, lakes, beaches, mountains, ancient ruins – one can go on and on. Italy makes you fall in love from the moment you step off the plane, every region is distinct and has its own charm, attractions, and cuisines, making it an ideal destination for all. Start your tour in Rome, home to the Vatican as well as countless sights, museums, and ancient ruins. Discover Tuscany and Florence, with Renaissance masterpieces such as Michelangelo’s "David" and Brunelleschi's Duomo and enjoy a gondola ride in Venice, the city of canals and treat yourself to an incredible shopping experience in Milan, Italy’s fashion capital. </p>
